OL,3,CPM cuts international aid to increase
OL,4,Cdefence spending to 2.5% of GDP by 2027
OL,6,FThe decision comes following rising
OL,7,Ftensions between Europe, the US and
OL,8,FRussia over the future of Ukraine, ITV
OL,9,FNews explains
OL,11,FPrime Minister Keir Starmer has
OL,12,Fslashed overseas aid spending to boost
OL,13,Fdefence to reach 2.5% of GDP within
OL,14,Fthe next two years.
OL,16,FStarmer said cutting aid wasn't a
OL,17,Fdecision he was "happy" to make but
OL,18,Fwas necessary in response to "tyrant"
OL,19,FVladimir Putin and uncertainty over US
OL,20,FPresident Donald Trump's commitment to
OL,21,FEuropean security.
