OL,6,FOverseas aid will be cut from 0.5% of
OL,7,Fgross national income to 0.3% by 2027
OL,8,F- a move that has already sparked
OL,9,Fbacklash from MPs and aid charities
OL,10,Fwho called it "short-sighted" and a
OL,11,F"betrayal of the world's most
OL,12,Fvulnerable children".
OL,14,FThe PM said the cut will help defence
OL,15,Fspending to rise from its current 2.3%
OL,16,Fshare of the economy to 2.5% in 2027.
