OL,6,FSetting out the plans in the Commons
OL,7,Fearlier, the PM said a "generational
OL,8,Fchallenge requires a generational
OL,9,Fresponse," adding: "That will demand
OL,10,Fsome extremely difficult and painful
OL,11,Fchoices.
OL,13,F"And through those choices, as hard as
OL,14,Fthey are, we must also seek unity, a
OL,15,Fwhole society effort that will reach
OL,16,Finto the lives, industries and the
OL,17,Fhomes of the British people."
