OL,6,FTrump has been demanding that Europe
OL,7,Fspends more on defence, while the
OL,8,Ftransatlantic approach to the war in
OL,9,FUkraine has come under strain after US
OL,10,Finterventions such as the US president
OL,11,Fsuggesting that Ukrainian President
OL,12,FVolodymyr Zelensky is a "dictator".
OL,14,FIt comes after ITV News' Robert Peston
OL,15,Frevealed the government would commit
OL,16,Fto increasing defence spending to 2.5%
OL,17,Fby the end of the decade - or much
OL,18,Fsooner - with Treasury and Downing
OL,19,FStreet officials working to get the
OL,20,Fnumbers together ahead of Starmer's
OL,21,Fmeeting with Donald Trump this week.
