OL,6,FSetting out the need for the UK to
OL,7,Frespond to Trump's push, the prime
OL,8,Fminister told MPs: "One of the great
OL,9,Flessons of our history is that
OL,10,Finstability in Europe will always wash
OL,11,Fup on our shores and that tyrants like
OL,12,FPutin only respond to strength."
